Saved!
Job Details
A Global association, communications and event Management Company is looking for a Creative production manager.Job responsibilities are:1. Responsible for Events- Conferences & Destination Management2. Handling Corporate Division and Public Sector clients3. Professionally and effectively employs sales skills to achieve targeted sales.4. Increase the level of sales and business mix from individual clients5. Increase share of each market sector6. Identify and develop sources of potential clients
Requirements
The candidate requirements:1. self-motivated person 2. Arabic speaking candidate.3. possess strong leadership qualities4. Excellent communication and negotiation skills5. The candidate should have Master’s degree6. Relevant experience within the industry
